fel.cvut.af.model.input

Class BasicOptionsInput

  • java.lang.Object
    • fel.cvut.af.model.input.Input
      • fel.cvut.af.model.input.BasicOptionsInput
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CheckboxGroupInput, RadioButtonGroupInput, SelectManyBasicOptionsInput, SelectOneBasicOptionsInput

    @MappedSuperclass
public abstract class BasicOptionsInput
extends Input
    An abstract class defines collection of Option for Input class.

    It is used for inputs where could be chosen from multiple options. For example SelectMany or RadioButtonGroup.
